<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ru">
    <head>
        <meta charset="UTF-8">
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
        <title>@ViewData["Title"] - SharpRise</title>
        <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
        <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
        <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
        <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/remixicon/4.6.0/remixicon.min.css">
        <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com/3.4.16"></script>
        <script src="~/js/tailwind.config.js"></script>
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="~/css/Index.css">
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="~/css/Login.css">
        </head>
    <body class="bg-[#0D1117]">
        </style>
<!-- Навигация -->
    <header class="fixed top-0 left-0 right-0 bg-[#161B22] border-b border-[#30363D] z-50">
        <nav class="container mx-auto px-6 py-4 flex items-center justify-between">
            <div class="flex items-center">
                <a href="#" class="text-3xl font-['JetBrains_Mono'] text-primary tracking-tight">&lt;SharpRise/&gt;</a>
                <div class="hidden md:flex ml-12 space-x-8">
                    <a href="#" class="text-gray-300 hover:text-primary font-medium">Обучение</a>
                    <a href="#" class="text-gray-300 hover:text-primary font-medium">Группы</a>
                    <a href="#" class="text-gray-300 hover:text-primary font-medium">Задачи</a>
                    <a href="#" class="text-gray-300 hover:text-primary font-medium">Документация</a>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center space-x-4">
                <button id="loginBtn" class="text-gray-300 hover:text-primary font-medium">Войти</button>
                <button id="registerBtn" class="bg-primary text-white px-5 py-2 !rounded-button whitespace-nowrap hover:bg-opacity-90 transition-all">Регистрация</button>
                <button class="md:hidden w-10 h-10 flex items-center justify-center text-gray-700">
                    <i class="ri-menu-line ri-lg"></i>
                </button>
            </div>
        </nav>
    </header>        

    @RenderBody()
    <!-- Подвал -->
    <footer class="bg-gray-900 text-white py-12">
        <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-4 gap-8 mb-8">
                <div>
                    <a href="#" class="text-2xl font-['Pacifico'] text-white mb-4 block">SharpRise</a>
                    <p class="text-gray-400 mt-2">Платформа для эффективного изучения C# с практическими задачами и групповым обучением.</p>
                    </div>
                        <div>
                            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-4">Платформа</h3>
                            <ul class="space-y-2">
                            <li><a href="#" class="text-gray-400 hover:text-white transition-colors">Обучение</a></li>
                            <li><a href="#" class="text-gray-400 hover:text-white transition-colors">Группы</a></li>
                            <li><a href="#" class="text-gray-400 hover:text-white transition-colors">Задачи</a></li>
                            <li><a href="#" class="text-gray-400 hover:text-white transition-colors">Документация</a></li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-4">Компания</h3>
                            <ul class="space-y-2">
                            <li><a href="#" class="text-gray-400 hover:text-white transition-colors">О нас</a></li>
                            <li><a href="#" class="text-gray-400 hover:text-white transition-colors">Карьера</a></li>
                            <li><a href="#" class="text-gray-400 hover:text-white transition-colors">Блог</a></li>
                            <li><a href="#" class="text-gray-400 hover:text-white transition-colors">Контакты</a></li>
                            </ul>
                            </div>
                        <div>
                            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-4">Связь с нами</h3>
                            <div class="flex space-x-4 mb-4">
                            <a href="#" class="w-10 h-10 flex items-center justify-center bg-gray-800 rounded-full hover:bg-primary transition-colors">
                            <i class="ri-telegram-fill"></i>
                            </a>
                            <a href="#" class="w-10 h-10 flex items-center justify-center bg-gray-800 rounded-full hover:bg-primary transition-colors">
                            <i class="ri-vk-fill"></i>
                            </a>
                            <a href="#" class="w-10 h-10 flex items-center justify-center bg-gray-800 rounded-full hover:bg-primary transition-colors">
                            <i class="ri-github-fill"></i>
                            </a>
                            <a href="#" class="w-10 h-10 flex items-center justify-center bg-gray-800 rounded-full hover:bg-primary transition-colors">
                            <i class="ri-youtube-fill"></i>
                            </a>
                        </div>
                        <p class="text-gray-400">info@sharprise.ru</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="border-t border-gray-800 pt-8 flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center">
                    <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm mb-4 md:mb-0">© 2025 SharpRise. Все права защищены.</p>
                    <div class="flex space-x-6">
                    <a href="#" class="text-gray-400 hover:text-white text-sm">Условия использования</a>
                    <a href="#" class="text-gray-400 hover:text-white text-sm">Политика конфиденциальности</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </footer>

<!-- Модальное окно входа -->
<div id="loginModal" class="fixed inset-0 z-50 hidden">
<div class="modal-overlay absolute inset-0"></div>
<div class="flex items-center justify-center min-h-screen p-4">
<div class="modal relative w-full max-w-md rounded-lg p-6 shadow-xl">
<button class="absolute top-4 right-4 text-gray-400 hover:text-white" id="closeLoginModal">
<div class="w-6 h-6 flex items-center justify-center">
<i class="ri-close-line ri-lg"></i>
</div>
</button>
<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6">Войти</h2>
<form>
<div class="mb-4">
<label class="block text-sm text-gray-400 mb-2">Email или имя пользователя</label>
<div class="relative">
<div class="absolute inset-y-0 left-0 pl-3 flex items-center pointer-events-none">
<div class="w-5 h-5 flex items-center justify-center text-gray-400">
<i class="ri-user-line"></i>
</div>
</div>
<input type="text" class="w-full bg-gray-800 border-none rounded py-2 pl-10 pr-3 text-white focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary focus:outline-none" placeholder="Введите email или имя пользователя">
</div>
</div>
<div class="mb-4">
<label class="block text-sm text-gray-400 mb-2">Пароль</label>
<div class="relative">
<div class="absolute inset-y-0 left-0 pl-3 flex items-center pointer-events-none">
<div class="w-5 h-5 flex items-center justify-center text-gray-400">
<i class="ri-lock-line"></i>
</div>
</div>
<input type="password" id="loginPassword" class="w-full bg-gray-800 border-none rounded py-2 pl-10 pr-10 text-white focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary focus:outline-none" placeholder="Введите пароль">
<button type="button" id="toggleLoginPassword" class="absolute inset-y-0 right-0 pr-3 flex items-center">
<div class="w-5 h-5 flex items-center justify-center text-gray-400">
<i class="ri-eye-off-line"></i>
</div>
</button>
</div>
</div>
<div class="flex items-center mb-6">
<div class="relative flex items-center">
<input type="checkbox" id="rememberMe" class="w-4 h-4 bg-gray-800 rounded border-gray-600 focus:ring-primary">
<div class="absolute w-4 h-4 bg-gray-800 rounded border border-gray-600 flex items-center justify-center" id="customCheckbox">
<div class="w-2 h-2 bg-primary rounded-sm hidden" id="checkboxIndicator"></div>
</div>
<label for="rememberMe" class="ml-2 text-sm text-gray-400 cursor-pointer">Запомнить меня</label>
</div>
<a href="#" class="ml-auto text-sm text-primary hover:text-opacity-80">Забыли пароль?</a>
</div>
<button type="submit" class="w-full bg-primary hover:bg-opacity-90 text-white py-2 px-4 rounded-button transition-colors !rounded-button whitespace-nowrap">Войти</button>
<div class="flex items-center my-6">
<div class="flex-grow h-px bg-gray-700"></div>
<span class="px-4 text-sm text-gray-400">или</span>
<div class="flex-grow h-px bg-gray-700"></div>
</div>
<button type="button" id="switchToRegister" class="w-full text-center text-primary hover:text-opacity-80">Зарегистрироваться</button>
</form>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<!-- Модальное окно регистрации -->
<div id="registerModal" class="fixed inset-0 z-50 hidden">
<div class="modal-overlay absolute inset-0"></div>
<div class="flex items-center justify-center min-h-screen p-4">
<div class="modal relative w-full max-w-md rounded-lg p-6 shadow-xl">
<button class="absolute top-4 right-4 text-gray-400 hover:text-white" id="closeRegisterModal">
<div class="w-6 h-6 flex items-center justify-center">
<i class="ri-close-line ri-lg"></i>
</div>
</button>
<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6">Регистрация</h2>
<form>
<div class="mb-4">
<label class="block text-sm text-gray-400 mb-2">Email</label>
<div class="relative">
<div class="absolute inset-y-0 left-0 pl-3 flex items-center pointer-events-none">
<div class="w-5 h-5 flex items-center justify-center text-gray-400">
<i class="ri-mail-line"></i>
</div>
</div>
<input type="email" class="w-full bg-gray-800 border-none rounded py-2 pl-10 pr-3 text-white focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary focus:outline-none" placeholder="Введите email">
</div>
</div>
<div class="mb-4">
<label class="block text-sm text-gray-400 mb-2">Имя пользователя</label>
<div class="relative">
<div class="absolute inset-y-0 left-0 pl-3 flex items-center pointer-events-none">
<div class="w-5 h-5 flex items-center justify-center text-gray-400">
<i class="ri-user-line"></i>
</div>
</div>
<input type="text" class="w-full bg-gray-800 border-none rounded py-2 pl-10 pr-3 text-white focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary focus:outline-none" placeholder="Введите имя пользователя">
</div>
</div>
<div class="mb-4">
<label class="block text-sm text-gray-400 mb-2">Пароль</label>
<div class="relative">
<div class="absolute inset-y-0 left-0 pl-3 flex items-center pointer-events-none">
<div class="w-5 h-5 flex items-center justify-center text-gray-400">
<i class="ri-lock-line"></i>
</div>
</div>
<input type="password" id="registerPassword" class="w-full bg-gray-800 border-none rounded py-2 pl-10 pr-10 text-white focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary focus:outline-none" placeholder="Введите пароль">
<button type="button" id="toggleRegisterPassword" class="absolute inset-y-0 right-0 pr-3 flex items-center">
<div class="w-5 h-5 flex items-center justify-center text-gray-400">
<i class="ri-eye-off-line"></i>
</div>
</button>
</div>
<div class="mt-2">
<div class="w-full h-1 bg-gray-800 rounded-full overflow-hidden">
<div id="passwordStrength" class="h-full bg-red-500 w-0 transition-all duration-300"></div>
</div>
<p id="passwordStrengthText" class="text-xs text-gray-400 mt-1">Минимум 8 символов</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="mb-6">
<label class="block text-sm text-gray-400 mb-2">Подтверждение пароля</label>
<div class="relative">
<div class="absolute inset-y-0 left-0 pl-3 flex items-center pointer-events-none">
<div class="w-5 h-5 flex items-center justify-center text-gray-400">
<i class="ri-lock-line"></i>
</div>
</div>
<input type="password" id="confirmPassword" class="w-full bg-gray-800 border-none rounded py-2 pl-10 pr-3 text-white focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary focus:outline-none" placeholder="Повторите пароль">
</div>
</div>
<div class="flex items-center mb-6">
<div class="relative flex items-center">
<input type="checkbox" id="termsAgree" class="w-4 h-4 bg-gray-800 rounded border-gray-600 focus:ring-primary">
<div class="absolute w-4 h-4 bg-gray-800 rounded border border-gray-600 flex items-center justify-center" id="termsCustomCheckbox">
<div class="w-2 h-2 bg-primary rounded-sm hidden" id="termsCheckboxIndicator"></div>
</div>
<label for="termsAgree" class="ml-2 text-sm text-gray-400 cursor-pointer">Я согласен с <a href="#" id="termsLink" class="text-primary hover:text-opacity-80">условиями использования</a></label>
</div>
</div>
<button type="submit" class="w-full bg-primary hover:bg-opacity-90 text-white py-2 px-4 rounded-button transition-colors !rounded-button whitespace-nowrap">Зарегистрироваться</button>
<div class="flex items-center my-6">
<div class="flex-grow h-px bg-gray-700"></div>
<span class="px-4 text-sm text-gray-400">или</span>
<div class="flex-grow h-px bg-gray-700"></div>
</div>
<button type="button" id="switchToLogin" class="w-full text-center text-primary hover:text-opacity-80">Уже есть аккаунт? Войти</button>
</form>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<!-- Модальное окно условий использования -->
<div id="termsModal" class="fixed inset-0 z-50 hidden">
<div class="modal-overlay absolute inset-0"></div>
<div class="flex items-center justify-center min-h-screen p-4">
<div class="modal relative w-full max-w-2xl rounded-lg p-6 shadow-xl">
<button class="absolute top-4 right-4 text-gray-400 hover:text-white" id="closeTermsModal">
<div class="w-6 h-6 flex items-center justify-center">
<i class="ri-close-line ri-lg"></i>
</div>
</button>
<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6">Условия использования</h2>
<div class="prose prose-invert max-h-[60vh] overflow-y-auto mb-6 text-gray-300">
<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">1. Общие положения</h3>
<p class="mb-4">Настоящие Условия использования регулируют отношения между SharpRise (далее - "Сервис") и пользователем сервиса (далее - "Пользователь").</p>
<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">2. Регистрация и использование</h3>
<p class="mb-4">2.1. Для использования Сервиса Пользователь должен зарегистрироваться, предоставив достоверную информацию.</p>
<p class="mb-4">2.2. Пользователь несет ответственность за сохранность своих учетных данных.</p>
<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">3. Правила поведения</h3>
<p class="mb-4">3.1. Пользователь обязуется не нарушать работу Сервиса.</p>
<p class="mb-4">3.2. Запрещено размещение материалов, нарушающих авторские права.</p>
<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">4. Конфиденциальность</h3>
<p class="mb-4">4.1. Сервис обязуется сохранять конфиденциальность личных данных Пользователя.</p>
<p class="mb-4">4.2. Пользователь соглашается на обработку персональных данных.</p>
<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">5. Ограничение ответственности</h3>
<p class="mb-4">5.1. Сервис предоставляется "как есть", без каких-либо гарантий.</p>
<p class="mb-4">5.2. Сервис не несет ответственности за любые убытки Пользователя.</p>
</div>
<button id="closeTermsBtn" class="w-full bg-primary hover:bg-opacity-90 text-white py-2 px-4 rounded-button transition-colors !rounded-button whitespace-nowrap">Закрыть</button>
</div>
</div>
</div>
    <!-- Скрипты для модальных окон -->
    <script src="~/js/Login/modalToggleScript.js"></script>
    <script src="~/js/Login/passwordStrengthScript.js"></script>
    <script src="~/js/Login/passwordToggleScript.js"></script>
    <script src="~/js/Login/customCheckboxScript.js"></script>

    </body>
</html>